<div style="margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: 700">Vouchers</div>

<p>This service allows you to create and manage digital vouchers in your retail operation.</p>

<p>Create a new voucher in this service, and your customer will receive an information email with a voucher code and voucher value. 
The voucher code, in the format "AA BB CC 11 22 33", is given to the cashier at checkout who will then redeem the code.</p>

<p>Redeem, or verify, a voucher by submitting the voucher code in the service interface. Customers will receive updates by email and all the activity will be logged, trackable in your service interface.</p>
    
<p>Functions included:</p>

<ul>
<li>Create digital vouchers with custom voucher values.</li>
<li>Redeem vouchers.</li>
<li>Verify status of voucher codes.</li>
<li>Track all voucher activities.</li>
</ul>
